readme:
# hubot-jira-prft

A hubot script that does the things

See [`src/jira-prft.coffee`](src/jira-prft.coffee) for full documentation.

## Installation

In hubot project repo, run:

`npm install hubot-jira-prft --save`

Then add **hubot-jira-prft** to your `external-scripts.json`:

```json
[
  "hubot-jira-prft"
]
```

## Sample Interaction

```
user1>> hubot hello
hubot>> hello!
```

## NPM Module

https://www.npmjs.com/package/hubot-jira-prft
